---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-16 text-center md:py-24">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute left-1/2 top-[-40px] -z-0 h-[400px] w-full max-w-[700px] -translate-x-1/2 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(217,119,6,0.08),transparent_60%)]"></div>
  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <span class="mb-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--bg-pill)] px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold text-[var(--ink-on-pill)]">
      <span class="rounded-full bg-accent px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-white">v0.0.1</span>
      Kubernetes operator
    </span>
    <h1 class="mx-auto mb-5 max-w-[14ch] font-heading text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">
      A <span class="text-accent">public IP</span> for every workload.
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mb-10 max-w-[60ch] text-base text-ink-muted sm:text-lg md:text-xl">
      frp-operator provisions cheap cloud exits and bin-packs your tunnels onto them, so any Service in any cluster gets a routable address — no matter what's blocking inbound on your side.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-stretch justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
      <a href="#install" class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white no-underline transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-accent-hi hover:shadow-md">
        Install
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" class="h-4 w-4"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="https://github.com/mtaku3/frp-operator" class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[var(--line-strong)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-ink no-underline transition hover:bg-[var(--bg-elev-2)]">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="h-[18px] w-[18px]"><path d="M12 .3a12 12 0 0 0-3.8 23.4c.6.1.8-.3.8-.6v-2c-3.3.7-4-1.6-4-1.6-.5-1.4-1.3-1.8-1.3-1.8-1.1-.7.1-.7.1-.7 1.2.1 1.8 1.3 1.8 1.3 1.1 1.8 2.8 1.3 3.5 1 .1-.8.4-1.3.8-1.6-2.7-.3-5.5-1.3-5.5-6 0-1.3.5-2.4 1.3-3.2-.1-.4-.6-1.6.1-3.2 0 0 1-.3 3.3 1.2a11.5 11.5 0 0 1 6 0c2.3-1.5 3.3-1.2 3.3-1.2.7 1.6.2 2.8.1 3.2.8.8 1.3 1.9 1.3 3.2 0 4.6-2.8 5.6-5.5 5.9.4.4.8 1.1.8 2.2v3.3c0 .3.2.7.8.6A12 12 0 0 0 12 .3"/></svg>
        GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
